Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper discusses monitoring virtualized resources and applications running on them, which involves distributed computing. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper mentions monitoring network resources in cloud computing environments. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses design issues related to engineering cloud monitoring tools. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper briefly mentions tracking leave and join operations of cloud resources due to failures, which can be related to security concerns. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses tracking Quality of Service (QoS) parameters related to various resources and applications, which can be related to control systems.
